{"tid":1259827,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳英特爾及美光等晶片商　續向華為供貨","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T18:48:07.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96292d86bcb4a206de9ce477ad3e378e2372ec49","tid":1259827,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"傳英特爾及美光等晶片商 續向華為供貨<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2958055/org/3fc67dcc7198bf1b33774609becd25b7.jpg/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2958055%2Forg%2F3fc67dcc7198bf1b33774609becd25b7.jpg%2Fimg%5D&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrtxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=0f0ff3aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2958055/org/3fc67dcc7198bf1b33774609becd25b7.jpg/img]</a><br />\n《紐約時報》引述消息人士消息報道，數家大型美國晶片商在特朗普政府針對華為的銷售禁令後，仍持續向華為出售相關組件，銷售額或高達數億美元。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，英特爾和美光(Micron)在內的美國晶片商，向華為提供美國以外地區生產的零件，令華為得以繼續生產智能手機及伺服器等產品。<br />\n<br />\n由於海外生產的貨品不被視為美國製造，故不受華府禁令影響，相關零件在3星期前已分批提供給華為。英特爾及美光拒絕回應相關報道。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部則重申，將華為加入實體清單，是防止違反國家安全或損害美國外交利益。"},{"pid":"a3b991e1f7ad59288e29e6ab2efa2cb30f4535e9","tid":1259827,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c1224b346083696a8a21030b801d2b4adc79c2","tid":1259827,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"FedEx提告美國商務部 真係精彩過啲劇集"}]}